1989;;Cold Comfort;;Canadian;;Vic Sarin;;Paul Gross, Maury Chaykin, Margaret Langrick;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cold_Comfort_(film);;Stephen Paul Gross is a salesman who gets drawn into a sexual psychodrama between Floyd (Maury Chaykin), a sociopathic truck driver, and his daughter Dolores (Margaret Langrick), when the three are caught together in a blizzard.